# DGL.ONLINE Brand Guidelines

Follow these brand guidelines when styling components and creating new UI elements.

## Brand Colors

### Primary Colors
| Name | Hex | Tailwind | Usage |
|------|-----|----------|-------|
| Orange | `#EA6B15` | `brand` / `brand-orange` | Primary actions, CTAs, highlights |
| Dark | `#1E1D1D` | `brand-dark` | Dark backgrounds, text on light |
| White | `#FFFFFF` | `white` | Light backgrounds, text on dark |

### Grayscale Palette
| Name | Hex | Tailwind | Usage |
|------|-----|----------|-------|
| Cloud | `#EDEFF7` | `gray-50` | Light backgrounds, muted areas |
| Smoke | `#D3D6E0` | `gray-100` | Borders, dividers |
| Steel | `#BCBFCC` | `gray-200` | Secondary borders |
| Space | `#9DA2B3` | `gray-300` | Muted text, icons |
| Graphite | `#6E7180` | `gray-400` | Secondary text |
| Arsenic | `#40424D` | `gray-500` | Dark mode borders/cards |
| Phantom | `#1E1E24` | `gray-600` | Dark mode background |
| Black | `#000000` | `gray-900` | Pure black (use sparingly) |

## Typography

**Primary Font:** Manrope (loaded via `next/font/google`)

### Type Scale
- H1: 64px (`text-6xl`) - Major headings
- H2: 48px (`text-5xl`) - Section headings
- Subheader 1: 32px (`text-3xl`) - Subsection titles
- Subheader 2: 24px (`text-2xl`) - Card titles
- Paragraph 1: 18px (`text-lg`) - Body text
- Paragraph 2: 16px (`text-base`) - Default text

### Font Weights
- Light: 300
- Regular: 400
- Medium: 500
- Semibold: 600
- Bold: 700
- ExtraBold: 800

## Logo Usage

### Available Logo Files
- `/public/logo.svg` - Primary (light background)
- `/public/logo-light.svg` - For dark backgrounds
- `/public/logo-icon.svg` - Icon only (dark)
- `/public/logo-icon-light.svg` - Icon only (light/white)

### Logo Guidelines
- Maintain 1/4 height clearspace around logos
- Don't stretch or distort logos
- Use appropriate variant for background color

## Color Usage Examples

```tsx
// Primary button
<button className="bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90">
  Action
</button>

// Dark sidebar
<aside className="bg-brand-dark text-white">
  <img src="/logo-light.svg" alt="DGL.ONLINE" />
</aside>

// Muted card
<div className="bg-muted text-muted-foreground">
  Secondary content
</div>

// Orange accent
<span className="text-brand">Highlighted text</span>
```

## CSS Variables (shadcn/ui)

The brand colors are configured as CSS variables in `globals.css` using HSL format for shadcn/ui compatibility:

- `--primary`: DGL Orange
- `--background`: White (light) / Phantom (dark)
- `--foreground`: Brand Dark (light) / Cloud (dark)
- `--muted`: Cloud (light) / Arsenic (dark)
- `--border`: Smoke (light) / Arsenic (dark)

